summary: This document appears to be a financial record related to Deutsche Bank's Wealth Management services, detailing account information and customer identification policies. It outlines the responsibilities of clients regarding their identification and compliance with financial regulations, including anti-money laundering laws.
keyFacts: The document discusses Deutsche Bank's customer identification policy and the requirements for establishing accounts.
It mentions the legal obligations of clients to provide accurate information regarding their identity and financial activities.
There are references to anti-money laundering regulations and the responsibilities of clients to report any changes in their information.
